    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Business enterprises centered on the printing press, having the main objective of printing books, journals, art prints, or other works. For enterprises having the primary objective of making printed products available to the public, but who may also print these products, use "publishing houses."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
